item.title: Imposible in 562 add music or some sounds?
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Not impossible, just unknown.
The 562 client isn’t exactly renamed/refactored like the 317 client is. You’d have to dig around in the client and figure out which packets handle the sounds… And then make them work server sided. Doing something like this isn’t exactly for beginners, so if you don’t know how to… Well, you’re not gonna have a good time.
